definition: faultless/complete/perfect/to leave nothing to be desired
to prepare/get ready/to provide or equip

sentences.english: This is why a man of perfect practice can accomplish everything.
sentences.chinese: 这就是修行完备的人做任何事都能善尽其功的原因。

sentences.english: Then the whole class space can be set up with the generating basis.

sentences.english: The weighted functions are obtained based on the use of completed systems of general solution of the corresponding homogeneous equations .

sentences.english: That the man of God may be complete, fully equipped for every good work.
sentences.chinese: 叫属神的人得以完备，为着各样的善工，装备齐全。

sentences.english: By contrast, Quine has taken but completeness into consideration while establishing standard logic.
sentences.chinese: 而蒯因在建立标准逻辑时仅仅考虑了完备性问题。

sentences.english: If lack of sex is going to disintegrate you, then go out and have a love-affair.
sentences.chinese: 如果缺少性的满足使你不完备，那么找一个对手去。

sentences.english: For example, no any examplebut affine hyperspheres is known so far.
sentences.chinese: 例如，人们甚至不知道是否有非完备仿射球的例子。

sentences.english: GIW offers a complete range of heavy-duty slurry pumps for FGD system scrubbers.
sentences.chinese: GIW为FGD系统洗涤器提供完备的重型泥浆泵。

sentences.english: Firstly, the attributes reduction algorithm is studied under the incomplete information systems.

sentences.english: Opponents will turn hesitation into complete obstruction.
sentences.chinese: 拦截者又尽没有犹豫天将入进完备壅闭。

sentences.english: Guarantee the staffs for their work and rights with fare-thee-well measurements.
sentences.chinese: 确保员工权及工作保障，并拟订完备之配套措施。

sentences.english: Hereby, the present authors think that Morse's normal-mode solution for the steady-state sound field in a room is complete.
sentences.chinese: 据此，认为简正波理论解是室内稳态声场的完备解。

sentences.english: Also, the maintainability of this system is good with full on-board test circuit.

sentences.english: Can Quantum-Mechanical Description of Physical Reality Be Considered Complete?
sentences.chinese: 物理现实的量子力学描述能否认为是完备的？

sentences.english: QS makes it feasible to deal with incomplete information effectively.
sentences.chinese: 定性仿真是处理不完备信息的有效方法。

sentences.english: The spirit of a man of perfect practice roams in the field of the formless.
sentences.chinese: 而修行完备的人是游心于此无形之境的。
